    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aerophones in which free reeds fitted in pipes or chambers are sounded individually or in combination by the player's blowing or sucking.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
